gamecontrollerd(8)           System Manager's Manual          gamecontrollerd(8)

NAME
     gamecontrollerd â€“ game controller daemon

SYNOPSIS
     gamecontrollerd

DESCRIPTION
     gamecontrollerd arbitrates access to hardware game controllers amongst apps
     using the GameController framework.

     There are no configuration options to gamecontrollerd . Users should not
     run gamecontrollerd manually.

FILES
     ~/Library/Preferences/com.apple.GameController.plist
         User's game controller settings.  Do not edit this file directly.

HISTORY
     gamecontrollerd was first introduced in Mac OS X version 10.9 (Mavericks).

SEE ALSO
     GameControllerConfigService(8)

